<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idc35dea6e-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1981-04-01">Apr. 1, 1981</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/96/466/s802/a/1">section 802(a)(1) of Pub. L. 96–466</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s3100">section 3100 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
